::Prowl::

He exits the Cybertronian Fire, aiming his weapons at Megaton.

"Identify yourself!" Prowl says, ready for battle once again, only 
this time he knew that in extreme cases he could transform into the 
giant beast that he had gotten from Iron Raptor.
